==English==

===Etymology===
From {{bor|en|fr|abandonnement}}, from {{m|fr|abandonner||to abandon, relinquish}}. {{m|fr|abandonner}} was originally equivalent to {{m|fr||mettre à bandon|to leave to the jurisdiction, i.e. of another}}, {{m|fr|bandon}} being from {{der|en|ML.|bandum}}, {{m|la|bannum||order, decree, ban}}. Equivalent to {{suffix|en|abandon|ment}}. (See also English {{m|en|banns}}.)

